  <section>
    <h2>Ruby Visibility Control</h2>
    <p>VB's <a href="/docs/i18n/">i18n system</a> provides a <code>data-ruby</code> attribute on <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> to control when annotations display:</p>

    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/ruby-visibility.html" url="ruby-visibility.html" title="Ruby visibility" shadow></browser-window>

    <table class="props-table">
